sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Task A
    participant B as Task B
    participant P as Pool 0.2.0
    participant C as Connection

    A->>P: acquire
    P->>C: open (cold)
    P-->>A: connection
    A->>C: stream 1 active
    B->>P: acquire
    P-->>B: same connection
    B->>C: stream 2 queued
    Note over C: max 1 concurrent stream
